  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Druid Domain Power</strong><br/><br/><p>At 8th level, you can project an aura of magically enhanced erosion as a standard action. Objects made primarily of metal or stone within this aura lose 10 points of hardness. Magic items retain a minimum hardness equal to twice their enhancement bonus and can attempt a Fortitude saving throw (DC = 10 + half your druid level + your Wisdom modifier) to negate this effect. A construct made primarily of metal or stone must succeed at a Fortitude save or lose all damage reduction and hardness for 1 round. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>",
